<h2>Changes in this release</h2>
<h3>Fixes</h3>
<ul>
<li>Fixed non-loading of AJAX-fetched content when using default theme (other themes unaffected)</li>
<li>Fixed rewriting of some tracked links</li>
<li>Fixed assignment of UUID to incorrect database table</li>
<li>Fixed incorrect UUID assignment to repeated messages. Thanks to <a href="https://www.phplist.org/our-team/duncanc/">Duncanc</a>. See the <a href="https://github.com/phpList/phplist3/pull/146" target="_blank">Pull Request</a>.</li>
<li>Fixed changed default password hashing algorithm</li>
<li>Replaced default Trevelin theme font to fix issue with some accented letters</li>
<li>Fixed missing help content in infoboxes</li>
</ul>
