<p>phpList 3.2.7 is a minor release including only one change.</p>
<h2>Changes in this release</h2>
<h3>PHPMailer Updated</h3>
<p>The <a href="https://github.com/PHPMailer/PHPMailer">PHPMailer</a> Library which is bundled inside phpList has been updated by the project&#8217;s developers to fix <a href="https://github.com/PHPMailer/PHPMailer/blob/v5.2.21/SECURITY.md">security vulnerabilities</a> which were discovered last month. phpList 3.2.7 includes an updated version of the library.</p>
<p><a href="https://github.com/PHPMailer/PHPMailer"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2957" src="https://www.phplist.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/phpmailer-logo-290x77.png" alt="PHPMailer Logo" width="290" height="77" srcset="https://www.phplist.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/phpmailer-logo-290x77.png 290w, https://www.phplist.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/phpmailer-logo.png 340w" sizes="(max-width: 290px) 100vw, 290px" /></a></p>
